column5: Hi all, Im looking to store a 17" boat anywhere east of Mississauga.  Any suggestions for lots.  Price helps.  Thanks  Steve
are you looking for storage for a couple of months or longer? do you want to be able to get your boat out of storage everytime you go fishing?
Yah, TJ doesn't charge by the word. How 'bout some details?
yeah, I would be picking it up and dropping it off in the summer and storing it in the winter.

Have you considered leaving it in a marina in the water and if you want to go to a different lake for the day just put it on the trailer and go. I think the marina's on Rice lake are about $700 for the year.(don't quote me on the price)
